<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="dark">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Payment Successful - ExtPay Manager</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com/3.4.1" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-950 text-slate-200 min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-4">
    <div class="w-full max-w-md bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-2xl text-center">
        <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-green-500/20 text-green-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-4xl mx-auto mb-6">
            ✓
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Payment Successful!</h1>
        <p class="text-slate-400 mb-8">Thank you for your purchase. Your license key is ready.</p>

        <div class="bg-slate-950 border border-slate-800 p-6 rounded-xl mb-8">
            <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2 font-mono">Your License Key</div>
            <div class="text-2xl font-mono font-bold text-blue-400 tracking-wider"><%= licenseKey %></div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-8">
            A copy of this key has been sent to <b><%= email %></b>.<br>
            Please copy this key and paste it into the extension to activate your features.
        </p>

        <button onclick="window.close()" class="w-full bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 text-white font-semibold py-3 rounded-lg transition-all">
            Close Window
        </button>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
